```

## CRITICAL Rules
- Feature flags default to `false` on errors (fail-closed)
- ALWAYS pass user context for percentage rollouts
- Use `LocalProvider` in development and tests â€” never call external services
- ALWAYS call `flags.shutdown()` during graceful shutdown
- Name flags with kebab-case: `feature-name`, not `featureName`

